;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502011501: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502011501.json-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' Heron Express, at your service! Have you made a delivery booking with us?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Who are you again?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115003-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I'm Ziqiao, a logistics specialist from Heron Express.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Delivery?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115005-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' That's right. For deliveries, please book a courier with Heron Express. I'm a Heron Express Specialist &mdash; Ziqiao's my name.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502115006-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115006-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' If you've got a delivery to send, please enter your shipping info via our Heron Express app. If you're waiting to receive a delivery, please wait for our courier cycranes' notification. If you'd like to send a delivery, please bring it to our office.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Courier cycranes are everywhere aboard the Xianzhou.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115008-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Haha, Xianzhou relies heavily on Heron Express Specialists: Delivering meals, online shopping, within-city deliveries... It'd be very difficult to operate Xianzhou without Heron Express.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Don't listen to all those claims about being able to stay indoors here. Without courier deliveries, do you really think anyone could stand staying in? Nobody could.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I saw a lot of parcels outside.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115011-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' This always gives me a headache. Some were put on hold due to cycrane failure; some were because the customer filled out their contact details incorrectly, so we couldn't get in touch with them.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' It may be my job to deal with these abandoned parcels, but there're just too many. If we can't track down the owner, we end up donating things to charity.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_502115013-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115013-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' But then again, I'm still on the clock right now. If you don't have anything to send right now, keep Heron Express in mind for next time. Our slogan is: Heron Express &mdash; We Mail Anything.
::'''Ziqiao:''' If there's nothing else, I'm getting back to work.
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 502011504: Config/Level/NPC/W2/NPC_DefaultStory_502011504.json-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' Oh, hi... I remember you. Have you booked a delivery with us?
::'''Ziqiao:''' We can do same-day delivery for small and medium packages. Big ones take two to three days, though. If you have any other requirements, please let us know.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404020202-->)
:{{DIcon|?}} I came across a depressed cycrane.
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 404020202: Config/Level/Mission/4040202/Act/Act404020202.json-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' A what cycrane?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} A depressed cycrane.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020252-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I know you said, "a depressed cycrane," but I don't understand what you mean.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} A malfunctioning cycrane.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020254-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' That I can understand, but I'll still trouble you to explain all of this to me in detail.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's the same model as this cycrane.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020256-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Uh-huh. You can see them all over Xianzhou. They handle deliveries... Why don't you tell me about what this "depressed" business is all about?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404020257-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020257-->
::You attempted to explain what you encountered as well as how you convinced this cycrane that had nothing left to live for to return to Heron Express.
::After listening to your story, Ziqiao examined the work status of courier cycranes. She discovered that everything you said could be verified. At that moment, a cycrane got reconnected to the logistics system.
::'''Ziqiao:''' Was it really able to speak with you? I can hardly believe it.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It's a warning of an AI awakening that will destroy mankind.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020261-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' An AI uprising? You aren't talking about the "Aurumaton Rebellion," are you? That happened before I was born. Take it easy. The Cloud Knights would never let something like that happen.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Besides, who knows. This cycrane is so pessimistic, it might destroy itself before it ever destroys humanity.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Or maybe it isn't willing to speak with you.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020264-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' ...I often speak with cycranes. Logically, they are completely open to me.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is it because you lack charm?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020266-->
::::'''Ziqiao:''' I can't be. I have been popular with people since I was young. When it comes to having charm, we would be well-matched with each other.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} No one would be so open with their own boss.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020268-->
::::'''Ziqiao:''' I'm not some boss. If I have to say it, these courier cycranes and I are more like coworkers.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Is it possible that you just don't know?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020270-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' ...I talk with cycranes frequently. If they could talk, they would have talked to me by now.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404020271-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020271-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' Besides, we never equipped these courier cycranes with any intelligence in the first place. The hardware components simply couldn't allow for it. Maybe you were just hearing things? Or perhaps someone was talking to you disguised as a cycrane?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Do you want to look into it more closely?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The way you said that makes me wonder if I really misheard the entire thing.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020274-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I'll look into it, just to be on the safe side.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404020275-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020275-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' Wait a moment. I'll check... Hold on. This isn't good!
::'''Ziqiao:''' Aside from the cycrane you mentioned, we've lost connection with several other cycranes... This isn't some kind of cycrane labor strike, is it?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} This must be the work of a competitor!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020278-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' You were suggesting that a competitor wanted to dismantle the courier cycranes and see their internal structure.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' ...Then they went a step further and made a version that could speak. Isn't that a technical skill that's better than the Technology Division of Heron Express?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} It was the work of a metal life form that could transform!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020281-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' The heliobi of the Heliobi Disaster were also life forms back then, and they were the ones that possessed the aurumatons' bodies... Your concerns did have some merit.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' However, if they are able to possess robotic bodies, then why not become something more ruthless?
:::'''Ziqiao:''' For example, a starskiff. A starskiff that could transform at will would have been far more impressive...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Your customers are bad news.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020285-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' You're saying that one of our customers might have made unauthorized modifications to the cycranes? There are loads of weird people on the Xianzhou Luofu. It's possible that someone went off the deep end and wanted to stir some trouble...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404020286-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020286-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' If that's the case, can I have you keep an eye out for me? If you come across any "malfunctioning cycranes," please bring them back. Is that OK?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_404020202_59-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_404020202_59-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I came to find you because I wanted a reward.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020288-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I haven't prepared any reward to give you... I might have been able to get something together if you said something earlier.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' ...Well. If you don't mind, I can treat you to a glass of Immortal's Delight.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Do you have any leads?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020291-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I've only just learned of this issue. How would I have any leads? I need to find time to investigate the matter.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Talk to me a little later.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll do my best.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404020294-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Great. I have a glass of unopened Immortal's Delight. I'll give it to you.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: 404020202_Finish-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404021701--> and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404020202-->)
:{{DIcon|?}} I found all the cycranes...
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 404021701: Config/Level/Mission/4040217/Act/Act404021701.json-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' Yes, yes, we've got all in the records here. All the missing cycranes have returned.
::'''Ziqiao:''' Here's a thank-you gift from the Heron Express for being our ace cycrane catcher.
::'''Ziqiao:''' Of course, you've mentioned before that these cycranes are actually equipped with intelligence &mdash; we've verified that this is indeed true. Every cycrane can produce coherent speech. It's quite astonishing.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You won't wipe their intelligence, will you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021706-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Who do you take us for here at Heron Express? We'd never do anything of the sort.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' They're required to undergo recruit training and as long as they don't break the law and can handle everyday work, who cares if cycranes have a little intelligence? I mean, lots of bots at the IPC have intelligence these days.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You must have realized that the first time one of them flew back.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021709-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Yes, but back then many of us had never even seen a cycrane speak before. We kept chatting with it until it became depressed.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Then it didn't speak for a long time, and it wasn't until the other cycranes came back to the system that we were able to verify everything.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404021711-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021711-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' We analyzed the missing cycranes' flight trajectories prior to losing contact. Once all the other flight paths were accounted for, there was only one suspicious trajectory left.
::'''Ziqiao:''' We tried getting in touch many times, but it wasn't willing to respond at all.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Did you go and make a claim for a refund?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021714-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Thanks to you, we didn't even end up suffering any damage &mdash; so we didn't need any compensation.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' But everyone still felt that they couldn't just act as if nothing had happened... In the final analysis, we just wanted to ask their designer why courier cycranes had been imbued with the gift of intelligence.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Since the designer was unwilling to give us a reply, we thought of you...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Report this kind of thing to the Realm-Keeping Commission, ASAP!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021718-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' We're not keen on involving the Realm-Keeping Commission here. And thanks to you, we didn't even end up suffering any damage.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' But everyone still felt that they couldn't just act as if nothing had happened... In the final analysis, we just wanted to ask their designer why courier cycranes had been imbued with the gift of intelligence.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Since the designer was unwilling to give us a reply, we thought of you...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Don't tell me you're asking for my help once more?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021722-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' You guessed correctly. You're the first person we thought of.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' We just wanted to ask the cycrane designer why courier cycranes had been imbued with the gift of intelligence.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_404021701_38-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_404021701_38-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm curious, too!
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021725-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I know, right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Some things are better off left unknown.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021727-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' No way. My curiosity is going to torment me until I find out.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Maybe the designer just wanted to troll us?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021729-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' "Just wanted to troll us," sure &mdash; I would be okay with that. I just want a definite answer here.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_404021730-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_404021730-->
::'''Ziqiao:''' As the ace cycrane catcher, I'd like you to write them a letter asking why. Of course, we'll protect any private information from being disclosed... But for sure we'll send the letter over.
