::{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you usually get up to around here?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115103-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I get asked that a lot, actually. After all, with this many cycranes aboard the Xianzhou, what do you need manual labor like me for?
:::'''Ziqiao:''' In actual fact, much of our work relies on human workforce: Inspecting goods, deploying cycrane routes, cycrane maintenance... plus all those pesky abandoned boxes you've seen on the streets...
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Oh yeah &mdash; there's another job that can only be done manually, and that's never going to change: Handling customer service complaints.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Is it true that you can really mail anything?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115107-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Sure. Our slogan is "Heron Express &mdash; We Mail Anything," but we reserve the right of final interpretation.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' We usually recommend that you avoid using robots if you're sending anything fragile or important. Instead, we recommend that you hire an armed escort service.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Before you finalize your order with us, please make sure you read our shipping regulations.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Logistics on Xianzhou is really something else.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115111-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' I know, right? You Outworlders have a much clearer perspective on this stuff than the Xianzhou natives. I'm always hearing old cranks say "Xianzhou is lifeless and never changes," but I disagree.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' It's just a hunch, but I've grown busier and busier these past two hundred years. Can you imagine? Around 150 years ago, down at the busy Starskiff Haven zone, we'd only be able to handle over 6400 cycrane deliveries per day.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' But just yesterday, there were... let me see... over 70,000 deployments over Starskiff Haven! And that's on a work day! Such a huge change in just 150 years.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's easy to miss if you're not paying attention. You've got quite the eye.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The logistics industry is becoming more and more important these days.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115116-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' You must also find that the more developed and convenient a city becomes, the more its citizens come to rely on logistical support. Today, Xianzhou can't afford to pause onboard logistics, and our burden is even heavier.
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Xianzhou is a massive giant, and our logistics system is its blood vessels. Our couriers keep its heart beating. Whenever I think of this, I'm filled with the feeling of being truly alive.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all. Keep up the good work.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_502115119-->
:::'''Ziqiao:''' Be careful out there, and remember &mdash; our slogan is "Heron Express &mdash; We Mail Anything."
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_502011502-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all. Keep up the good work.
::'''Ziqiao:''' Be careful out there, and remember &mdash; our slogan is "Heron Express &mdash; We Mail Anything."
