::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Cash-on-delivery?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Could there be a mistake?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} C'mon, it's a chest!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_412260207-->
